{"id": "1230744955346096259", "channel_id": "1230480070293061673", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "這單純是介面風格統一性問題，可能出現在任何其他地方。相位對弈製作週期較快，也相對其他系統更新，投入資源也更少，這方面更容易出這樣的問題。", "timestamp": "2024-04-19T05:01:03.490000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230480070293061673", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：相位对弈正式版即将发布", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1230745076984975451", "channel_id": "1230480070293061673", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "介面表現各方面目前可能會不盡人意，但是好玩了之後會再逐步改進！", "timestamp": "2024-04-19T05:01:32.491000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230480070293061673", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：相位对弈正式版即将发布", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
